### Blair MacIntyre's Github pages.

I have some personal pages here.  Georgia Tech has an enterprise Github server, where we keep most of our work.  My lab (@aetatgt) also has a set of public repositories here.

### Contact
My home webpage is at http://blairmacintyre.me or contact me via my Georgia Tech email at blair@cc.gatech.edu
